### 🎵 Pruebas del Nuevo Sistema ChordPro

### 1. Crear canción con ChordPro (SÚPER FÁCIL!)
POST http://localhost:3000/songs/chordpro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chordProText": "{title: Amazing Grace}\n{artist: Traditional}\n{key: G}\n\n[G]Amazing [G7]grace how [C]sweet the [G]sound\nThat [G]saved a [D]wretch like [G]me\n[G]I once was [G7]lost but [C]now I'm [G]found\nWas [G]blind but [D]now I [G]see"
}

### 2. Crear canción moderna
POST http://localhost:3000/songs/chordpro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chordProText": "{title: How Great Thou Art}\n{artist: Stuart K. Hine}\n{key: C}\n\n[C]O Lord my [F]God when [C]I in awesome wonder\n[Am]Consider [F]all the [G]worlds thy hands have [C]made\n[C]I see the [F]stars I [C]hear the rolling thunder\n[Am]Thy power through[F]out the [G]universe dis[C]played\n\nThen sings my [F]soul my [C]savior God to [Am]thee\n[F]How great thou [C]art how [G]great thou [C]art\nThen sings my [F]soul my [C]savior God to [Am]thee\n[F]How great thou [C]art how [G]great thou [C]art"
}

### 3. Obtener todas las canciones
GET http://localhost:3000/songs

### 4. Exportar canción a ChordPro (usar ID de la canción creada)
GET http://localhost:3000/songs/SONG_ID_HERE/chordpro

### 5. Comparación: Crear con método tradicional (MUY TEDIOSO)
POST http://localhost:3000/songs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Método Tradicional",
  "artist": "Tedioso",
  "key": "C",
  "lyricsLines": [
    {
      "text": "Amazing grace how sweet the sound",
      "chords": [
        { "note": "C", "index": 0 },
        { "note": "C7", "index": 8 },
        { "note": "F", "index": 18 },
        { "note": "C", "index": 29 }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
